# Exit Intent Revenue Calculator

A sophisticated, mobile-optimized exit intent popup calculator designed for service-based businesses to calculate annual revenue potential from dormant customers, including cost-of-waiting analysis for enhanced urgency messaging.

## Overview

This calculator helps businesses discover their hidden revenue goldmine by analyzing their existing customer database potential. It calculates 12-month revenue projections based on customer reactivation campaigns and provides powerful urgency messaging through cost-of-delay calculations.

## Features

### Core Functionality
- **6-Step Interactive Process**: Guided data collection for accurate projections
- **Advanced Revenue Modeling**: 12-month projections with email fatigue and database growth
- **Cost of Waiting Analysis**: Weekly delay costs with enhanced urgency for paid advertising businesses
- **Industry-Specific Optimization**: Tailored starting values for 9 business types
- **Mobile-First Design**: Optimized for mobile exit intent scenarios

### Technical Features
- **Single File Implementation**: No external dependencies
- **Responsive Design**: Works on all device sizes
- **A/B Testing Ready**: 11 randomized header variations
- **FTC Compliant**: Legal disclaimers and earnings statements
- **Analytics Ready**: Built-in tracking points for conversion optimization

## Quick Start

### 1. Download and Deploy
```bash
# Download the calculator file
wget https://youroutsourcecmo.com/calculator/exit-intent-calculator.html

# Deploy to your web server
cp exit-intent-calculator.html /var/www/html/
```

### 2. Configure Results Page
Update the redirect URL in the calculator:
```javascript
// Line 847 in calculateAdvancedRevenue() function
const revealUrl = `https://yourdomain.com/big-reveal.html?${params.toString()}`;
```

### 3. Implement Exit Intent Trigger
```javascript
// Basic exit intent detection
let exitIntentShown = false;

document.addEventListener('mouseleave', function(e) {
    if (e.clientY <= 0 && !exitIntentShown) {
        showExitIntentCalculator();
        exitIntentShown = true;
    }
});

function showExitIntentCalculator() {
    // Load calculator iframe or popup
    const calculatorFrame = document.createElement('iframe');
    calculatorFrame.src = '/exit-intent-calculator.html';
    calculatorFrame.style.cssText = 'position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:none;z-index:999999;';
    document.body.appendChild(calculatorFrame);
}
```

